                                                                                              senior leaders and executives are to manage security and privacy risks (including supply chain risks) to
                                                                                              organizational operations, organizational assets, individuals, other organizations, and the Nation. The risk
                                                                                              management strategy includes an expression of organizational risk tolerance; acceptable risk assessment
                                                                                              methodologies and risk response strategies; a process for consistently evaluating security and privacy
